node.text:
Happy birthday to my twin!
We have far surpassed friendship, and have become more like sisters. I love you beyond words and can’t wait to celebrate you tonight. Lets be real we celebrate you like 3 times a week and it’s my favorite thing to do. Keep being the brightest star in the room . ILY @tkempss
